feat: add Docker container monitoring API endpoints (fl-4ya)

Add REST endpoints for Docker container monitoring:
- GET /api/{project_id}/containers - list containers
- GET /api/{project_id}/containers/{id}/checks - check history
- GET /api/{project_id}/containers/{id}/stats - current snapshot
- GET/PUT /api/{project_id}/settings/docker - threshold overrides
- GET /api/v1/system/containers - admin list all

Includes DB layer methods for querying monitored_containers,
container_checks, container_monitor_state, and project
docker_thresholds. Follows existing api.go patterns with RBAC
via requireRole middleware.

